            <h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:chad_solomon@catalystsoftwaresolutions.com">chad_solomon@catalystsoftwaresolutions.com</a></p>

            <div class="terms-notice">
                <strong>Note:</strong> These general terms apply to the use of our website. Specific service engagements will be governed by separate, detailed service agreements.
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    .terms-container {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .terms-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--catalyst-orange) 0%, var(--catalyst-blue) 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 80px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .lead {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .terms-content {
        padding: 60px 20px;
        background: white;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .last-updated {
        background: var(--off-white);
        padding: 16px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--catalyst-orange);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .terms-content h2 {
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .terms-content p {
        color: var(--text-gray);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .terms-content ul {
        color: var(--text-gray);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        padding-left: 24px;
    }

    .terms-content li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .terms-content a {
        color: var(--catalyst-blue);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .terms-content a:hover {
        color: var(--catalyst-orange);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .terms-notice {
        background: rgba(242, 106, 44, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--catalyst-orange);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .terms-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
